---
export interface Props {
  formUrl: string;
  waUrl: string;
}

const { formUrl, waUrl } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="mt-12">
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-eg-azul-dark to-eg-azul text-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-white mb-3">¿Listo para sumarte?</h2>
    <p class="text-white/85 mb-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      La preinscripción no implica compromiso de pago. Te asegura prioridad de cupo para la próxima cohorte.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a href={formUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-eg-primary">Preinscribirme</a>
      <a href={waUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-eg bg-white/15 text-white border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/25 hover:no-underline">Consultar por WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
